=== 總統選舉 ===
{{Main|2016年美國總統選舉}}
在2016年11月8日大选日，特朗普获得306张[[美国选举人团|选举人票]]，民主党对手希拉里·克林顿获得232张，12月19日選舉人進行投票，因为[[失信选举人|两边都出现选举人叛变]]，数字被減少至304票和227票，同时正式将特朗普选为总统，於2017年1月6日獲美國國會確認最終的選舉結果。<ref>{{cite news |first1=Kiersten |last1=Schmidt |first2=Wilson |last2=Andrews |title=A Historic Number of Electors Defected, and Most Were Supposed to Vote for Clinton |date=2016-12-19 |accessdate=2017-01-31 |website=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2016/12/19/us/elections/electoral-college-results.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170125123736/https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2016/12/19/us/elections/electoral-college-results.html |archive-date=2017-01-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

特朗普比克林顿获得更少的普选票，使他成为{{le|第五位输掉普选却成为总统的人|United States presidential elections in which the winner lost the popular vote}}，这种现象的历史可追溯到1824年。<ref>Desilver, Drew. "[http://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2016/12/20/why-electoral-college-landslides-are-easier-to-win-than-popular-vote-ones/ Trump's victory another example of how Electoral College wins are bigger than popular vote ones] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2016/12/20/why-electoral-college-landslides-are-easier-to-win-than-popular-vote-ones/ |date=20170130010257 }}", [[皮尤研究中心|Pew Research Center]] (December 20, 2017).</ref>克林顿多获得了286万张选票，或2.1个百分点，相较特朗普为48.04%对46.09%，而都未在全国范围内获得[[多數決原則|绝对多数]]的选票。<ref>{{cite news |first=Greg |last=Price |title=Popular Vote Update: Why Hillary Clinton Didn't Win A Majority Of The Electorate |date=2016-11-17 |website=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]] |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/popular-vote-update-why-hillary-clinton-didnt-win-majority-electorate-2447571 |access-date=2017-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101001939/http://www.ibtimes.com/popular-vote-update-why-hillary-clinton-didnt-win-majority-electorate-2447571 |archive-date=2017-01-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="LeipAtlas2016PrezResults">{{cite news |last=Leip |first=David |date=2016-12-20 |title=2016 Presidential General Election Results |url=http://uselectionatlas.org/RESULTS/index.html |newspaper={{tsl|en|Dave Leip's Atlas of U.S. Presidential Elections|}} |location=Newton, Massachusetts |accessdate=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229043829/http://uselectionatlas.org/RESULTS/index.html |archive-date=2016-12-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

特朗普的胜利被认为是一次政治逆转。虽然特朗普的民调长期落后于民主党候选人希拉里·克林顿，且她确实赢得更多普選票数，但在多数[[摇摆州|摇摆州]]，特朗普的支持度在竞选活动中被低估。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.politico.com/story/2016/11/election-results-2016-clinton-trump-231070 |title=Trump pulls off biggest upset in U.S. history |publisher=[[Politico|Politico]] |date=2016-11-09 |first=Maxwell |last=Tani |accessdate=2016-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109080707/http://www.politico.com/story/2016/11/election-results-2016-clinton-trump-231070 |archive-date=2016-11-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

特朗普赢得了大多數的摇摆州如[[佛罗里达|佛罗里达]]、[[愛荷華|愛荷華]]和[[俄亥俄|俄亥俄]]，并翻转了克林顿的“{{link-en|蓝色长城 (政治)|Blue wall (politics)|蓝色长城}}”州如[[密歇根|密歇根]]、[[宾夕法尼亚|宾夕法尼亚]]和[[威斯康星|威斯康星]]，它们自1992年（威斯康辛為1988年）以来就一直支持民主党。

