===放寬無人機暗殺活動===
奥巴马總統時期CIA的[[無人機|無人機]]暗殺活動達到前任八倍，中情局被授權展开“特征空袭作戰”（signature strikes），根据行为模式与[[人際关系|人際关系]]推論來攻击未完全确认身份的“恐怖分子”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jul/01/obama-continue-signature-strikes-drones-civilian-deaths |title=US to continue 'signature strikes' |access-date=2019-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190308080906/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jul/01/obama-continue-signature-strikes-drones-civilian-deaths |archive-date=2019-03-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這直接導致多國無辜民眾死傷直線上升，奥巴马後期發現此一現象的國際輿論反撲，於是2016年7月通過命令要求美国国家情报总监公布一份公開報告顯示無人機攻擊下平民死傷數字和論述<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2016/04/05/obamas-most-dangerous-drone-tactic-is-here-to-stay/ |title=外交政策雜誌-Obama’s Most Dangerous Drone Tactic Is Here to Stay |access-date=2019-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190308080815/https://foreignpolicy.com/2016/04/05/obamas-most-dangerous-drone-tactic-is-here-to-stay/ |archive-date=2019-03-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2012/11/02/counting-civilian-casualties-in-cias-drone-war/ |title=外交政策雜誌-Counting civilian casualties in CIA’s drone war |access-date=2019-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502035638/https://foreignpolicy.com/2012/11/02/counting-civilian-casualties-in-cias-drone-war/ |archive-date=2019-05-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以此部分制約CIA的行動，雖然諸多國家對此報告數字誠實度有所質疑，然而此報告還是某種程度揭露了美國無人機暗殺行動。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mintpressnews.com/report-1-in-3-deaths-caused-by-us-drone-strikes-this-year-in-yemen-were-civilians/252058/ |title=MPN - killed by U.S. drone strikes  |access-date=2019-03-07 |archive-date=2021-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206042726/https://www.mintpressnews.com/report-1-in-3-deaths-caused-by-us-drone-strikes-this-year-in-yemen-were-civilians/252058/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根據伦敦新闻调查社的報告整理，2009至2015年間美國承認在[[中東|中東]]無人機暗殺約4200人，其中約800人是平民被誤殺，但報告中也未闡述證明其餘三千多人如何確認是“恐怖分子”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mondialisation.ca/pakistan-yemen-somalia-libya-obamas-drone-casualty-numbers-conceals-extensive-us-war-crimes/5533994 |title=mondialisation.ca - Obama’s Drone |access-date=2019-03-07 |archive-date=2021-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210816092708/https://www.mondialisation.ca/pakistan-yemen-somalia-libya-obamas-drone-casualty-numbers-conceals-extensive-us-war-crimes/5533994 |dead-url=no }}</ref>川普總統上台後開始大舉放鬆CIA無人機使用自主權，認為現有規章還是束縛性太高，2017年初川普造访中情局向时任局长蓬佩奥表示，希望能采取“更激进”的空袭行动以打擊美國敵人，兩個月後川普将[[也门|也门]]与索马里划定为“战事激烈区”在此處的無人機行動可不受歐巴馬條約原則管束。2019年3月川普宣布無人機平民死傷數字報告廢除，因為「敵人也會閱讀，並用以對美國不利」從此美國不再公布無人機暗殺行動中的平民死傷數。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://new.qq.com/omn/20190307/20190307A0ZGKC.html |title=特朗普签行政令：平民伤亡别公开了 敌人会看 |access-date=2019-03-07 |archive-date=2021-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212090740/https://new.qq.com/omn/20190307/20190307A0ZGKC.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/executive-order-revocation-reporting-requirement/ |title=白宮行政命令-Executive Order on Revocation of Reporting Requirement |access-date=2019-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190307205709/https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/executive-order-revocation-reporting-requirement/ |archive-date=2019-03-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

