==== 健保法案 ====

在競選過程中，川普發誓要廢除和替換[[患者保护与平价医疗法案|歐記健保]]，而在上任總統後不久，川普也立即敦促國會這麼做。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Trump Can Kill Obamacare With Or Without Help From Congress|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2016/11/09/501203831/trump-can-kill-obamacare-with-or-without-help-from-congress|accessdate=2020-11-08|author=|date=2016-11-09|format=|work=NPR.org|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2017-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120035046/http://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2016/11/09/501203831/trump-can-kill-obamacare-with-or-without-help-from-congress|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年5月，由共和黨控制的眾議院通過了以黨派形式投票廢除歐記健保另立[[2017年美国保健法案|川普保健法案]]的立法<ref>{{Cite web|title=House passes ObamaCare repeal|url=https://thehill.com/policy/healthcare/331937-house-passes-obamacare-repeal|accessdate=2020-11-08|date=2017-05-04|last=Smilowitz|first=Elliot|work=TheHill|language=en|archive-date=2017-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170725082904/http://thehill.com/policy/healthcare/331937-house-passes-obamacare-repeal|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但由於在參議院表決時3名共和黨籍參議員[[約翰·麥凱恩|約翰·麥凱恩]]、[[蘇珊·柯琳絲|蘇珊·柯琳斯]]和[[麗莎·穆爾科斯基|麗莎·穆爾科斯基]]跑票反對廢除歐記健保，再加上所有民主黨籍參議員的反對，廢除歐記健保的提議在參議院中以49:51的票數遭到了否決。<ref>{{Cite web|title=共和黨跑票 廢除歐記健保失敗 川普：讓它內爆|url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2146281|accessdate=2020-11-08|author=|date=2017-07-28|last=|format=|work=自由時報|publisher=|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103074207/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2146281|dead-url=no}}</ref>

儘管未能廢除歐記健保，川普仍透過簽署行政命令和法案削弱歐記健保，2017年川普簽署的《[[2017年减税与就业法案|2017年減稅與就業法案]]》中規定自2019年起廢除[[患者保护与平价医疗法案|歐記健保]]中違反個人強制納保的罰款。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Without the Insurance Mandate, Health Care’s Future May Be in Doubt (Published 2017)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/12/18/us/politics/tax-cut-obamacare-individual-mandate-repeal.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2017-12-18|accessdate=2020-11-08|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Robert|last=Pear|archive-date=2017-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224155456/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/12/18/us/politics/tax-cut-obamacare-individual-mandate-repeal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，國會把所謂的{{En-link|凱迪拉克保險單|Cadillac insurance plan}}醫療保險福利稅、醫療器械消費稅和醫療保險稅三項保險稅取消。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Trump signs bill repealing ACA Cadillac tax, granting 'relief' for employers|url=https://www.hrdive.com/news/trump-signs-bill-repealing-aca-cadillac-tax-granting-relief-for-employer/569551/|accessdate=2020-11-08|author=|date=2019-12-23|format=|work=HR Dive|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191224203130/https://www.hrdive.com/news/trump-signs-bill-repealing-aca-cadillac-tax-granting-relief-for-employer/569551/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而川普在其總統任內也未曾放棄廢除歐記健保的打算，並上訴至[[美国最高法院|美國最高法院]]。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Trump Administration Asks Supreme Court to Strike Down Affordable Care Act|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/26/us/politics/obamacare-trump-administration-supreme-court.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-09-24|accessdate=2020-11-08|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Sheryl Gay|last=Stolberg|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103045141/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/26/us/politics/obamacare-trump-administration-supreme-court.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 減稅法案 ====
2017年12月，川普簽署了[[2017年减税与就业法案|2017年減稅與就業法案]]，將公司稅率永久降低到21％，將個人所得稅率降低直到2025年，同時也增加了兒童稅收抵免額，將{{En-link|美國的遺產稅免|Estate tax in the United States}}稅額增加了一倍，達到1,120萬美元，並將州和地方稅收減免限制為10,000美元。<ref>{{Cite news|title=What’s in the Final Republican Tax Bill (Published 2017)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/12/15/us/politics/final-republican-tax-bill-cuts.html,%20https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/12/15/us/politics/final-republican-tax-bill-cuts.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2017-12-15|accessdate=2020-11-06|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Wilson|last=Andrews|first2=Alicia|last2=Parlapiano}}</ref>

==== 國内經濟 ====
自[[2007年–2008年環球金融危機|2008年金融海嘯]]後，從2009年6月開始的經濟擴張期一直持續到2020年2月因[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]導致的經濟衰退，是美國歷史上持續時間最長的經濟成長。<ref>{{Cite news|title=The U.S. Entered a Recession in February|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/08/business/economy/us-economy-recession-2020.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-06-30|accessdate=2020-11-06|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Jeanna|last=Smialek|archive-date=2020-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609223239/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/08/business/economy/us-economy-recession-2020.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>川普则常强调在他的帶領下，美国金融市场和經濟達到了歷史最佳，尤其以[[道琼斯指数|道琼斯指数]]是衡量成功的标。道琼斯指数衡量30家在美国证券交易所上市的大公司业绩，确实在2020年初创下历史新高。然而股市隨後因為COVID-19疫情影響導致的[[2020年国际金融恐慌|金融恐慌]]而崩盤，它的崩盘也抹去了川普就职以来取得的所有成就。<ref>{{Cite news|title=美国大选前，六张图帮你看懂特朗普任期内的国民经济|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-54282875|newspaper=BBC News 中文|accessdate=2020-12-29|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103073531/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-54282875|dead-url=no}}</ref>

