edaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170209/1052122//|publisher=《臺灣蘋果日報》|accessdate=2017-02-09|date=2017-02-09|language=zh|location=臺北市|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211155403/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170209/1052122//|archive-date=2017-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>9日當晚與習近平通話後表示，美國將加強與中國之間的關係，並認同「[[一個中國政策|一個中國政策]]」（Honor America's long-standing "One China" policy）<ref>{{cite pressrelease|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2017/02/09/readout-presidents-call-president-xi-jinping-china|title=Readout of the President’s Call with President Xi Jinping of China|date=2017-02-09|publisher=Office of the Press Secretary, The White House|language=en|location=Washington D.C.|quote=The two leaders discussed numerous topics and President Trump agreed, at the request of President Xi, to honor our "one China" policy.|access-date=2017-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213002548/https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2017/02/09/readout-presidents-call-president-xi-jinping-china|archive-date=2017-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時雙方也互相邀請對方來自己國家會面。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20170210/trump-xi-call-one-china-policy/zh-hant/|title=川普與習近平通電話：認同「一個中國」政策|publisher=The New York Times 《紐約時報》|language=zh|date=2017-02-10|quote=「兩位領導人討論了許多話題。在習近平主席的要求下，川普總統同意履行我們的一個中國政策，」白宮在週四深夜發佈的一份聲明中表示。文中還稱這次談話「格外親切友好」，兩位領導「都邀請對方來自己國家會面」。|location=華盛頓特區|access-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170212200539/http://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20170210/trump-xi-call-one-china-policy/zh-hant|archive-date=2017-02-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://nyti.ms/2kRT6iE|script-title=en:Trump Tells Xi Jinping U.S. Will Honor ‘One China’ Policy|author1=Mark Landler|author2=Michael Forsythe|date=2017-02-09|publisher=The New York Times《紐約時報》|language=en|location=Washington D.C.|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216220657/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/02/09/world/asia/donald-trump-china-xi-jinping-letter.html?smid=pl-share|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://usat.ly/2kad5oH|title=Trump tells Xi Jinping: U.S. will honor 'One China' policy|author=Charles Ventura|publisher=USA Today《今日美國報》|date=2017-02-09|language=en|quote=President Trump spoke to Chinese President Xi Jinping for the first time since taking over the White House late Thursday, agreeing to honor America's long-standing "One China" policy.}}</ref>而川習會後中美開始轉為緩和關係，川普較少著墨，並派團參加了歐巴馬時代抵制的[[一帶一路|一帶一路]]活動。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.worldjournal.com/4990184/article-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3-5%E5%B9%B4%E6%8B%9A8%E5%85%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83/# |title=中國擴大對美國進口 5年拚8兆美元 |access-date=2017-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623165713/https://www.worldjournal.com/4990184/article-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3-5%E5%B9%B4%E6%8B%9A8%E5%85%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83/ |archive-date=2018-06-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

