2017年時[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國|朝鮮]]的核武器越來越被視為嚴重威脅。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title=North Korea crisis: How actions have unfolded under Trump|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/north-korea-crisis-how-events-have-unfolded-under-trump-n753996|accessdate=2020-11-07|work=NBC News|language=en|dead-url=no|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809191204/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/north-korea-crisis-how-events-have-unfolded-under-trump-n753996}}</ref> 2017年8月川普警告朝鮮並威脅將以「世界從未見過的火與怒」來應對朝鮮的核威脅。朝鮮作出回應發布朝鮮計畫試驗發射導彈至[[關島|關島]]附近。<ref>{{Cite news|title=North Korea details Guam strike plan and calls Trump 'bereft of reason'|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/aug/10/north-korea-details-guam-strike-trump-load-of-nonsense|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2017-08-10|accessdate=2020-11-07|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|first=Julian|last=Borger|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103074655/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/aug/10/north-korea-details-guam-strike-trump-load-of-nonsense|dead-url=no}}</ref>川普在2017年9月的聯合國大會上中表示，為了捍衛美國或其盟國，美國將「徹底摧毀朝鮮」。同年9月，川普加大了對朝鮮的制裁力度，宣布他希望朝鮮實現「完全無核化」。<ref name="#1"/> 2018年1月時金正恩表示整個美國都在朝鮮的導彈射程範圍內，川普則回擊他的核按鈕比金正恩的更大顆。<ref>{{Cite web|title=川普嗆金正恩：我的核按鈕比你更大！|url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2300944|accessdate=2020-11-07|author=|date=2018-01-03|last=|format=|work=自由時報電子報|publisher=|language=zh-TW|dead-url=no|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103074713/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2300944}}</ref>然而在這段朝美緊張時期之後，川普和金正恩至少交換了27封信，川普將其形容為「情書」，其中描述了兩人的親密友誼。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Transcript: Kim Jong Un's letters to President Trump|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/09/09/politics/transcripts-kim-jong-un-letters-trump/index.html|accessdate=2020-11-07|work=CNN|dead-url=no|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103074731/https://www.cnn.com/2020/09/09/politics/transcripts-kim-jong-un-letters-trump/index.html}}</ref>另外，2017年4月，川普曾在接受[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]採訪時，說在剛結束的美中首腦會談上，中國的[[習近平|習近平]][[中國國家主席|主席]]曾對他表示「朝鮮在古代曾是中國的一部分」（Korea actually used to be a part of China），對此[[韓國外交部|韓國外交部]]表示該發言「沒有考慮的價值」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=트럼프 "한국은 역사적으로 중국의 일부였다더라"|url=https://www.joongang.co.kr/article/21490349|access-date=2022-05-03|date=2017-04-19|last=기자|first=정은혜|work=중앙일보|language=ko|archive-date=2022-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524012639/https://www.joongang.co.kr/article/21490349}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=“한국은 사실상 중국 일부였다” 시진핑, 트럼프에게 충격 발언|url=https://www.joongang.co.kr/article/21494144|access-date=2022-05-03|date=2017-04-20|last=기자|first=이경희 기자 정은혜|work=중앙일보|language=ko|archive-date=2022-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524014235/https://www.joongang.co.kr/article/21494144}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=정부 "한국이 중국의 일부? 일고의 가치도 없다"|url=https://www.joongang.co.kr/article/21493253|access-date=2022-05-03|date=2017-04-19|last=기자|first=이지상|work=중앙일보|language=ko|archive-date=2022-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524014238/https://www.joongang.co.kr/article/21493253}}</ref>

2018年初朝鮮開始向[[大韩民国|韓國]]和美國釋出善意，同年3月川普同意了金正恩的會議提議。<ref>{{Cite news|title=With Snap ‘Yes’ in Oval Office, Trump Gambles on North Korea (Published 2018)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/03/10/world/asia/trump-north-korea.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2018-03-10|accessdate=2020-11-07|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Peter|last=Baker|first2=Choe|last2=Sang-Hun|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113074401/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/03/10/world/asia/trump-north-korea.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年6月川普和金正恩在新加坡進行[[2018年朝美首脑会晤|會晤]]。金正恩重申了他「致力於朝鮮半島完全無核化」的目標，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Read the Agreement Signed by President Trump and Kim Jong Un|url=https://time.com/5309425/donald-trump-kim-jong-un-summit-document-full-text/|accessdate=2020-11-07|author=|date=2018-06-12|format=|work=Time|publisher=|language=En|dead-url=no|archive-date=2020-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200608203739/https://time.com/5309425/donald-trump-kim-jong-un-summit-document-full-text/}}</ref>但是在2019年2月在[[河內市|河內]]舉行的[[2019年2月朝美首腦會談|朝美首腦會談]]未經協議而突然終止。兩國互相指責對方並且對於談判有不同的說法。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Trump’s Talks With Kim Jong-un Collapse, and Both Sides Point Fingers (Published 2019)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/02/28/world/asia/trump-kim-vietnam-summit.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2019-02-28|accessdate=2020-11-07|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Edward|last=Wong|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228222211/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/02/28/world/asia/trump-kim-vietnam-summit.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年6月，川普、金正恩和[[韓國總統|韓國總統]][[文在寅|文在寅]]在[[朝韩非军事区|朝韓非軍事區]]舉行[[2019年美韓朝三方會談|簡短會談]]；在[[板門店|板門店]]，川普越過[[三八綫|三八綫]]與金正恩握手，成爲首位踏上朝鮮領土的美國現任總統。<ref>{{cite news |author1=加洛 |title=特朗普跨越板門店分界線進入朝鮮會見金正恩 |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-dmz-meet-kim-20190701/4980294.html |accessdate=2022-01-16 |agency=美國之音 |date=2019-07-01 |archive-date=2022-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220310200759/https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-dmz-meet-kim-20190701/4980294.html }}</ref>川普和金正恩同意恢復談判，但是同年10月的雙邊談判沒有成功。<ref>{{Cite web|title=North Korea Says Nuclear Talks Break Down, US Says Went Good {{!}} Time|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007060513/https://time.com/5693526/north-korea-us-nuclear-diplomacy-sweden/|accessdate=2020-11-07|date=2019-10-07|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>由於朝美雙方對於美國解除朝鮮的經濟制裁和無核化談判等關鍵議題上皆未能取得共識，朝鮮威脅將再度開啟長程[[导弹|導彈]]的測試，朝美關係再度陷入僵局。<ref>{{Cite web|title=北韓批美國不談非核化 揚言將不遵守停止核試承諾|url=https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4301484|accessdate=2020-11-07|author=|date=2020-01-21|last=|format=|work=聯合新聞網|publisher=|language=zh-TW|dead-url=no|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103080358/https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4301484}}</ref>

