litics/us-refugee-cap-fy21/index.html|access-date=2021-05-04|last=CNN|first=Jennifer Hansler and Priscilla Alvarez|work=CNN|archive-date=2021-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627013152/https://www.cnn.com/2020/10/01/politics/us-refugee-cap-fy21/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这项政策直到2021年5月才被改變，美国总统拜登宣布将接纳庇护人数提升至62,500人<ref>{{Cite news|title=Biden increases US refugee cap to 62,500 amid backlash over earlier plan – as it happened|first2=Adam|first5=Sam|last4=Aratani|first4=Lauren|last3=Bergman|first3=Megan Mayhew|last2=Gabbatt|last=Singh|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/live/2021/may/03/joe-biden-politics-live-coronavirus-covid-politics-latest|first=Maanvi|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|accessdate=2021-05-04|date=2021-05-04|newspaper=The Guardian|last5=Levin|archive-date=2021-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627013121/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/live/2021/may/03/joe-biden-politics-live-coronavirus-covid-politics-latest|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 限制穆斯林移民 ===
{{main|第13769号行政命令}}
