川普後來澄清身為[[美國公民|美國公民]]或在[[美軍|美軍]]服役的穆斯林不在此限，仍然可以進入美國。<ref>"Trump's plan would block all Muslims from entering the United States, with an exception for U.S. citizens who are Muslim, who would come and go as they wish... 'If a person is a Muslim, goes overseas and comes back, they can come back. They're a citizen. That's different,' Trump said.", [http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/donald-trump-stands-barring-muslims-criticism/story?id=35640361 "Donald Trump Stands by Barring Muslims Despite Bipartisan Criticism"] {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/donald-trump-stands-barring-muslims-criticism/story?id=35640361 |date=20170121160211 }}, John Santucci, ABC News, December 8, 2015.</ref>特朗普提議的措施是臨時性質，<ref name="auto1"/>等到有了「更好的甄別方法」就可以終止。<ref name="auto2"/>

