cans who have abandoned Donald Trump |url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/oct/08/donald-trump-list-of-republicans-reject-support-endorsement?CMP=share_btn_tw |work=The Guardian |date=2016-10-08 |access-date=2017-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104180308/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/oct/08/donald-trump-list-of-republicans-reject-support-endorsement?CMP=share_btn_tw |archive-date=2016-11-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。參議院中接近三分之一的共和黨員表示不會投給川普<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2016-10-11/trump-says-it-s-hard-to-do-well-with-zero-support-from-ryan |title=Trump’s Attacks on GOP Leaders Ignite Civil War Inside Party |publisher=Bloomberg News |date=2016-10-11 |accessdate=2016-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011145435/http://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2016-10-11/trump-says-it-s-hard-to-do-well-with-zero-support-from-ryan |archive-date=2016-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但也有許多共和黨的議員仍然支持川普<ref name="Support">{{cite news |last1=Scott |first1=Eugene |title=Where Republicans stand on Trump |url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/08/politics/donald-trump-video-women-remarks-republicans/ |accessdate=2016-10-08 |publisher=CNN |date=2016-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008172847/http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/08/politics/donald-trump-video-women-remarks-republicans/ |archive-date=2016-10-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有數十位共和黨議員要求川普退選，讓他的副總統參選人彭斯接手<ref name="BlakeGrowingList">{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2016/10/07/the-gops-brutal-responses-to-the-new-trump-video-broken-down |title=Here’s the fast-growing list of Republicans calling for Donald Trump to drop out |last=Blake |first=Aaron |date=2016-10-08 |work=The Washington Post |accessdate=2016-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008050253/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2016/10/07/the-gops-brutal-responses-to-the-new-trump-video-broken-down/ |archive-date=2016-10-08 |dead-url=n